<p>The <code>@border</code> property returns TRUE if this is the first OR last iteration.</p>

<h2>Highlight First and Last</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  &lt;span {open}@border ? style="font-weight:bold"{close}&gt;{open}$colors{close}&lt;/span&gt;
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<p>
{colors}
  <span {@border ? style="font-weight:bold"}>{$colors}</span>{@notLast ? , }
{/colors}
</p>

<h2>Special Styling for Borders</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}@border{close}
    &lt;li style="background:#ff0"&gt;{open}$name{close} (border)&lt;/li&gt;
  {open}else{close}
    &lt;li&gt;{open}$name{close}&lt;/li&gt;
  {open}/@border{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<ul>
{users}
  {@border}
    <li style="background:#ff0">{$name} (border)</li>
  {else}
    <li>{$name}</li>
  {/@border}
{/users}
</ul>
